no relation to the former state chairman of the republican party of texas , susan weddington   sarah ragle weddington ( born february 5 , 1945 ) , is an american attorney , law professor , and former member of the texas house of representatives best known for representing " jane roe " ( real name norma mccorvey ) in the landmark roe v. wade case before the united states supreme court .

notable women : sarah weddington was the attorney who successfully argued this landmark supreme court case in 1973

